<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 85. Clubiona spp. of the C. ternatensis group (A-E) and the C. trivialis group (F), epigyne, cleared, ventral view A C. mii sp. nov., holotype B C. subkuu C C. theoblicki D C. tongi E C. zhengi F C. bicornis. Abbreviations: A = atrium; CO = copulatory opening; R = epigynal ridge. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 57. Clubiona spp. of the C. ternatensis group, male palp, ventral view A C. theoblicki B C. tongi C C. subkuu D C. subtongi sp. nov., holotype E C. zhengi. Abbreviations: E = embolus; EB = embolar base; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis; TH = tegular hump. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 77. Clubiona spp. of the C. ternatensis group (A-E) and the C. trivialis group (F), epigyne, intact, ventral view A C. mii sp. nov. holotype B C. subkuu C C. theoblicki D C. tongi E C. zhengi F C. bicornis. Abbreviations: A = atrium; CO = copulatory opening; R = epigynal ridge. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 93. Clubiona spp. of the C. ternatensis group (A-E) and the C. trivialis group (F), vulva, cleared, dorsal view A C. mii sp. nov., holotype B C. subkuu C C. theoblicki D C. tongi E C. zhengi F C. bicornis. Abbreviations: BS = bursa; CD = copulatory duct; FD = fertilisation duct; SP = spermatheca. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 67. Clubiona spp. of the C. ternatensis group, male palp, retrolateral view A C. theoblicki B C. tongi C C. subkuu D C. subtongi sp. nov., holotype E C. zhengi. Abbreviations: E = embolus; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis; VTA = ventral tibial apophysis. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535502" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535486" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535494" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535476" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535466" .

